  "title": "Robotica",
  "description": "Robotica is a futuristic Minecraft mod set in a high-tech world filled with advanced robots, towering mechs, and powerful sci-fi weapons",
  "body": "<!-- LOGO + SOCIALS -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xTSNugI.png\" alt=\"Main Banner\">\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\" alt=\"Divider\">\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/TJc3CxR4jK\">\n        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Discord&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=white\">\n    </a>\n    &nbsp;\n    <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@nightbeamstudio\">\n        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=YouTube&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=youtube&logoColor=white\">\n    </a>\n    &nbsp;\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/sponsors/MeherBenSalem\">\n        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=GitHub&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=github&logoColor=white\">\n    </a>\n    &nbsp;\n    <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/nightbeamstudio/projects\">\n        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=CurseForge&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=white\">\n    </a>\n    &nbsp;\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/organization/nightbeam\">\n        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Modrinth&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=white\">\n    </a>\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- ABOUT HEADER -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/about.png\">\n</p>\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/cSrvJJl5D0k\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<!-- KOFI -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/nightbeamstudio\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c14e387dab576fe667689cf/670f5a0171bfb928b21a7e00_support_me_on_kofi_beige.png\" width=\"350\">\n    </a>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n    The Year 3001 brings a high-tech, cyber-futuristic world filled with machines, robotics, and advanced crafting.\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- FEATURES HEADER -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/features.png\">\n</p>\n\n\n<!-- FEATURES CONTENT -->\n### Upgradeable Mechs\nConstruct and pilot towering mechanical suits built for exploration and combat.\n\n* Customize loadouts with interchangeable **Upgrade Cards**.\n* Boost attack power, mobility, armor plating, or enable auto-repair.\n* Swap upgrades on the fly for different biomes, bosses, or PvP.\n\n### Extended Crafting System\nGo beyond vanilla recipes with a tech-driven progression.\n\n* Refine **Scrap**, craft **PCBs**, and assemble **Electrical Conduits**.\n* Unlock late-game schematics: plasma cannons, energy cells, and more.\n\n### Robots & Custom Entities\nA world filled with autonomous life.\n\n* Encounter **RobotMK1** sentries, **BogieMK1** scouts, and prototypes.\n* Deploy your own drones, turrets, or mining bots.\n\n### Immersive Futuristic World\n* Explore neon cities, derelict factories, and research outposts.\n* Fight rogue AI and rival mech pilots while uncovering hidden lore.\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- RECIPES -->\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center;\">Recipes</h1>\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n    <p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Dhk80gG.png\"></p>\n    <p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dPdKPHQ.png\"></p>\n    <p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/633dF3x.png\"></p>\n    <p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hp98JhL.png\"></p>\n    <p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ifSAqCD.png\"></p>\n</div>\n\n<!-- MOBS -->\n<h1 style=\"text-align:center;\">Mobs</h1>\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n    <p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qk2CVsL.png\"></p>\n    <p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XJkpacR.png\"></p>\n    <p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VzBrBwb.png\"></p>\n</div>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/installation.png\">\n</p>\n\n<!-- INSTALLATION -->\n<div>\n    <p><strong>⏩ Minecraft 1.16.5, 1.18.2, 1.19.2, 1.20.1, 1.21.1, 1.21.5, 1.21.8</strong></p>\n    <p><strong>⏩ NeoForge or Forge</strong></p>\n    <p><strong>⏩ JAUMl Library</strong></p>\n</div>\n",
